  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "使用说明 · 压测复盘对比看板",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## 压测复盘对比看板\n\n本看板专为**多次压测之间的横向对比**与**单场压测复盘**设计,与常规监控的 `出价压测面板.json` 互补。\n\n### 推荐操作流程\n\n1. **打标 (annotation)**: 在每次压测开始/结束时,在任意 panel 标题右侧菜单或图表上点 `Add annotation`,**Tag 必须包含 `loadtest`**,并附带场景描述,如 `1000QPS-单拍品`、`1500QPS-多拍品-batch=20`。看板的 `压测开始/结束 (tag=loadtest)` annotations 会自动把所有标记渲染到所有图上。\n2. **单场详细复盘**: 把 dashboard 顶部时间范围调到**该次压测的窗口**(例如 `2026-06-04 14:00 → 14:30`),所有【单场窗口】行的 panel 显示该次的 P50/P95/P99、accepted/rejected、阶段耗时、Redis 隔离效果、worker 落库情况。\n3. **跨场次叠加对比**: 把时间范围调到**几天**(`now-7d` 或更长),【长周期总览】行的 ACK P95 / QPS 曲线会把每一次压测的尖峰自然画在同一张图里,配合 annotation 即可一眼看出哪次压测峰值更高/更稳。\n4. **填变量(可选)**: 顶部 `run_a_label` / `run_a_start` / `run_a_end` 等 textbox 变量,仅作为本次复盘的**文字标签**展示在 Notes panel 中,方便截图归档(Grafana 不支持把任意 unix 时间戳变量直接传进 PromQL 做 time-shift,故未做查询级叠加)。\n\n### 截图清单(报告配图建议)\n\n- 长周期 ACK P95(配 annotation,展示每次压测尖峰)\n- 单场:出价请求按 result 速率\n- 单场:阶段耗时 P95 by stage\n- 单场:Lua 脚本 P95 by script\n- 单场:Redis 命令 P95 by instance(rt-* / rt-worker-* / pubsub-* / ranking-* / cache 隔离效果)\n- 单场:连接池 wait_count + timeouts\n- 单场:bid_record / bid_ranking worker 消费速率\n- 单场:goroutine / RSS / CPU\n\n### 当前对比的场次(填了变量后会显示在最底部 Notes panel)\n\n- A: `${run_a_label}` (开始 `${run_a_start}` 结束 `${run_a_end}`)\n- B: `${run_b_label}` (开始 `${run_b_start}` 结束 `${run_b_end}`)\n- C: `${run_c_label}` (开始 `${run_c_start}` 结束 `${run_c_end}`)\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "行1 · 长周期总览 (跨场次自然叠加,把时间范围调到 now-7d 即可)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "长周期 出价 ACK P95 (跨场次尖峰对比)",
      "description": "把 dashboard 时间范围调到几天,所有压测期间的 ACK P95 尖峰会在同一张图上自然叠加,配合 tag=loadtest 的 annotation 即可定位每次压测窗口。",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "ms",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] },
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["max", "lastNotNull"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "(histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(aieas_auction_bid_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "ack p95",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "(histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(aieas_auction_bid_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "ack p99",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
